  (text "Use the OpenRX-Shared library alias for imported symbols, footprints, and 3D models.\nNext capture pass on this sheet: place U3/U1/Y1/U2/Y2/ANT1, then add the passive network exactly from OpenRX-Lite/SCHEMATIC.md."
